  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IsDefaultsBoxAnnotation, IsDefaultsEllipseAnnotation, IsDefaultsLineAnnotation, IsDefaultsPointAnnotation, IsDefaultsXYAnnotation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAnnotation, AbstractXYAnnotation, BoxAnnotation, DefaultBox, DefaultEllipse, DefaultLine, DefaultPoint, EllipseAnnotation, LineAnnotation, PointAnnotation
